items.text: 3. Access specific telemetry in the follower and leader tabs above. Each of these tabs have additional sub tabs with different types of telemetry.
1. Once opening the Mission Control Layout, wait for all the graphs to load in. This may take a while.
2. Refrain from reloading the page as this requires reloading all the graphs. There is no need for reloading as real time telemetry is sent to graphs directly.
4. Limit to 1 or 2 people on the Layouts at a time as to not overload the backend server.
5. You may also navigate the layout tree on the left in the My Items folder to view individual graphs and layout tabs without having to load in the entire set of layouts and graphs.
